library(igraph)
set.seed(38)
#dev.off() # reset the graphics device
g<-graph.adjacency(termmatrix , weighted = T , mode ="undirected")

plot(g ,
     vertex.color ="green",
     vertex.size = 2,
     edge.color ="red" ,
     vertex.label.cex = 0.8,
     edge.arrow.size = 0.1,
     
     )

# remove self loop using simplified function
sim_g<- simplify(g)
#set a vertices  level with name of g
V(sim_g)$label<-V(sim_g)$name
V(sim_g)$degree<-degree(sim_g)
